<div style="text-align:justify">
<section>
        <p>The mission of our research group is to make <em>rigorous, relevant and elegant</em> contributions to the scientific knowledge of humanity. We use computational, mathematical and biophysical approaches to figure out how living cells use <em>force, space and time</em> in their <em>problem-solving strategies</em>. We work so that the basic science discoveries we make become part of the <em>worldwide, multi-generational tapestry</em> of scientific knowledge that benefits all.</p>
      </section>
